{"tid":532869,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"VAR 視像執法","createTime":"2018-01-18T08:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T01:28:01.000Z","uid":97364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a2d541a94f76209c88dcad3a9612ec38eb46b55e","tid":532869,"uid":97364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T08:46:36.000Z","msg":"廢事騎劫咗人地個post，開一個post 講下var 執法<br />\n<br />\n洲際盃試行，好多地方都開始效法，我唔知係資源不足定點，都做唔返洲際盃果個效果 (洲際盃都有d鳩野，但整體算係咁)。<br />\n<br />\n洲際盃現埸影住出面有2-3個人監察住埸波，好多野會提點主球證，好想知其他聯賽其實有冇咁人力去做呢樣野，定一般靠晒個球證去判同決定去睇var，有睇開澳職既賭撚，應該會知佢地用var 有幾垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nvar明明係好野，都可以俾d 球證搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h9Z_dXhrPQU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dh9Z_dXhrPQU&d=s09NBRW2RjhpgeTTQya5GuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=49f20c13\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h9Z_dXhrPQU</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gA8JVwnywD4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgA8JVwnywD4&d=s09NBRW2RjhpgeTTQya5GuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=0e4c7f77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gA8JVwnywD4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qJiZHeAeDgI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqJiZHeAeDgI&d=s09NBRW2RjhpgeTTQya5GuargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=c5421ed9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qJiZHeAeDgI</a><br />\n<br />\n好多領隊會話有var 就唔會發生d 誤判，其實個球證鳩，就算有var 都可以好撚鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ccc57fb846b7cfeeeb418cfa75e3d251de2560f","tid":532869,"uid":7